; Regression test for issue #615: auto xacts at beginning of journal seen as uncleared (BZ#615)
; https://github.com/ledger/ledger/issues/615
;
; When auto transactions (=) appear at the beginning of a journal, --cleared and --uncleared
; filters should correctly reflect the cleared status of the parent transaction, not treat
; the auto-generated postings as uncleared.

= /Expenses/
    [Budget:Expenses]  (-1)
    [Budget:Available]  (1)

2024/01/01 * Cleared paycheck
    Expenses:Food    $10.00
    Assets:Cash     $-10.00

test reg --cleared
24-Jan-01 Cleared paycheck      Expenses:Food                $10.00       $10.00
                                Assets:Cash                 $-10.00            0
                                [Budget:Expenses]           $-10.00      $-10.00
                                [Budget:Available]           $10.00            0
end test

test reg --uncleared
end test
